cs.LO, cs.GT, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with formal verification of probabilistic systems using mathematical logic.
- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is also likely as the paper discusses turn-based stochastic games with limsup and liminf objectives.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper presents polynomial-time algorithms for computing the values of Markov decision processes.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper deals with decision-making in probabilistic systems.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with control of probabilistic systems.
